-- Lehman not in talks for sale: source
-- 
-- Wed Jun 18, 2008 10:26am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/06/18/us-lehmanbrothers-sale-idUSWEN633520080618

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Lehman Brothers Holdings Inc LEH.N is not in talks for a sale of the company, and Chief Executive Richard Fuld is not considering a sale, a person close to the firm said on Wednesday. 

 Earlier, CNBC cited Wall Street insiders as saying Fuld was weighing a sale. (Reporting by  Paritosh Bansal ; Editing by Lisa Von Ahn)